#: ../../K/kluge-up.rst:5
msgid "kluge up"
msgstr "kluge up"

#: ../../K/kluge-up.rst:7
msgid "vt\\."
msgstr "他動詞"

#: ../../K/kluge-up.rst:9
msgid ""
"To lash together a quick hack to perform a task; this is milder than "
":ref:`cruft-together` and has some of the connotations of :ref:`hack-up` "
"(note, however, that the construction kluge on corresponding to :ref:`hack-"
"on` is never used). \"I've kluged up this routine to dump the buffer "
"contents to a safe place.\""
msgstr ""
"あるタスクを実行するために手早いハックを寄せ集めること。これは\\ :ref:`cruft-together`\\ よりは穏やかで、\\ "
":ref:`hack-up`\\ の含意をいくらか持つ(ただし、\\ :ref:`hack-on`\\ に対応するkluge "
"onという言い回しは決して使われないことに注意)。「バッファの内容を安全な場所にダンプするこのルーチンをkluge upした」。"
